<Content>Good Budget Hotel near tram Good bargain rate hotel.Positives: 2 blocks to tram stop (20 minutes by tram to downtown Berlin)McDonalds a 2 minute walk for a good, cheap breakfastRoom was large with big windows.Free parking behind building for 10 cars; otherwise parking is available on street.Negatives: Small bathroomRoom was stuffy in August and open window was noisyTHE INTERNET IS NOT FREE AS ADVERTISED. IT IS A NORMAL T-MOBILE HOT SPOT 
