<Content>COLD! I was there for 2 last days of December. I was quite disappointed with this post-Soviet hotel where heating was not working: after 1 full day(!) they fixed it (a receptionist did it) ... I had an impression that they knew exactly what the problem was but they just wanted to save money on heating!The only good thing is the location (very close to S-Bahn station Adlershof, just between central/east Berlin and Schonefeld airport). 
