<Author>srilankalovers
<Content>Value for money Just returned from a three night stay at Berolina airport hotel Berlin. Met German friends who also stayed at this hotel. We all agree that if you are looking for a budget clean bed, hot shower and good continental breakfast in a basic hotel without any frills (or even evening meals being offered!) this hotel is fine. Very much a case of you get what you pay for If you want luxury, high level of comfort and service, pay more and stay somewhere posher!! We found Susies Bistro next door to this hotel served very good evening meals at very good prices with good service. Many people in hotel did the same. We cannot complain with value for money. Hope this helps! 
